Package: ScEnsemble
Title: Ensemble Clustering for Single-Cell RNA-seq Data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person("Beste", "Uncu", email = "besteuncu@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Ä°dil", "Yavuz", role=c("aut")))
Description: This package applies multiple individual and ensemble clustering 
    algorithms to single-cell RNA-seq data with integrated validation and 
    visualization tools. It implements k-means, hierarchical clustering,
    spectral clustering, and Leiden clustering algorithms, 
    combining their results using hypergraph-based ensemble approaches.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports: 
    methods, cluster, fpc, clValid, clusterCrit, SingleCellExperiment, SC3, 
    SIMLR, Seurat, cidr, ggplot2, igraph, mclust, scRNAseq, Rtsne, stats, 
    monocle3, RaceID, RColorBrewer, clusterSim, corrplot, dplyr, ggalluvial, 
    gridExtra, plotly, tidyr, uwot, viridis, SummarizedExperiment
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
